description: This Dart file defines a class named 'Note' representing a note entity used in a note organizer application. It includes properties for note attributes, a factory constructor to instantiate from a map, and a method to serialize it back to a map.

classes.name: Note
classes.description: Represents a single note with properties for id, title, content, createdAt, and updatedAt; with methods for serialization and deserialization.

methods.name: Note.fromMap
methods.description: Factory constructor that creates a Note instance from a Map<String, dynamic> object, parsing date strings into DateTime objects.

methods.name: toMap
methods.description: Serializes the Note object into a Map<String, dynamic>, with an option to include the id field.
